PRIVACY POLICY FOR BEYOND FIT

Last updated: January 28, 2026

INTRODUCTION
Beyond Fit ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information in our iOS application.

DATA COLLECTION
Beyond Fit does NOT collect, store, or transmit any personal data to external servers. All workout data, exercise information, and user preferences are stored locally on your device using iOS's UserDefaults system.

INFORMATION STORED LOCALLY
The following data is stored only on your device:
- Workout routines and exercises
- Workout history and progress
- Nutrition tracking data
- User preferences (units, notifications)
- Custom exercises you create

This data remains on your device and is never transmitted to us or any third parties.

DATA SECURITY
Since all data is stored locally on your device, your information is protected by your device's security measures (passcode, Face ID, Touch ID).

THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
Beyond Fit does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

CHILDREN'S PRIVACY
Beyond Fit does not knowingly collect data from children under 13. Our app is designed for users who are at least 13 years old.

CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected with an updated "Last updated" date.

CONTACT US
